ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectDesignated Barley - August 1, 2010 - July 31, 2011.*** INITIAL PAYMENT ***
PrecisOrder establishing the initial payments for barley of the grades, other than the base grade, selected and accepted for use in the production of barley flour, barley malt or pot or pearled barley for deliveries to THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD during the pool period commencing on August 1, 2010 and ending on July 31, 2011.
